Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
On behalf of Charter Hall, CBRE & Knight Frank are pleased to present For Lease the latest release in the successful Motorway Industrial Park, Berrinba.  

Located only 30 minutes from the Brisbane Port and Airport, 25 minutes from the Brisbane CBD and situated on the Logan Motorway with access via the recently upgraded Wembley Road interchange.  

After the recent completion of warehouses for Mitre 10 and QLS Logistics there are three remaining stages offering the following: 
•	Flexible designs accommodating tenancies from 11,000sqm* to 24,800sqm +*
•	Stage 1 – Building 3: 11,300sqm* 
•	Stage 1 - Building 4: 16,500sqm*
•	Stage 2 – Building 5: 12,362sqm* – 24,802sqm*
•	Stage 3 – Building 6: 8,615sqm – 17,230sqm*     
•	Open plan, A-grade offices and amenities 
•	Multiple driveway crossovers and separate access for staff/ visitors  
•	Minimum 10.5m* springing height – 13.7m* ridge height.  
•	Up to 39m* all-weather awning for hardstand loading & 42m* hardstand depths 
•	Recessed loading docks with levellers (if required) 
•	ESFR fire suppression systems  
•	Excellent Motorway exposure for signage opportunities 
•	Early site works now complete
*Approx.

Berrinba is an established, prime industrial and logistics hub within South East Queensland. It’s a preferred location for interstate distribution given proximity to major transport routes and manufacturing users for its ability to draw on a skilled, local workforce.     

Contact the agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.

CBRE are proud to present one of South East Queensland’s most exciting mixed-use developments currently under construction – Berrinba Central.  This major multi-stage development is prominently located on the corners of Browns Plains Road, Wayne Goss Drive and Peter Way, where it benefits from outstanding exposure and access to over 30,000 cars daily.
 
A multitude of major national brands have already committed to the development, including United Petroleum, Starbucks, Pie Face, Bridgestone and Sparkles Car Wash, plus more to be announced soon.  Flexible tenancy areas are now leasing from 250sqm to 3,000sqm and are suitable for a wide range of uses including large format retail, automotive, trade retail, indoor sport and recreation, medical / healthcare, childcare and more (STCA).
 
The development is centrally located between Brisbane, Gold Coast and Ipswich, with easy access to the Logan Motorway and the Mount Lindesay Highway.  It is only metres from the Woolworths anchored ‘Marsden on Fifth’ Shopping Centre, and is surrounded by high-growth residential suburbs and major retail / commercial hubs such as Browns Plains, Heritage Park, Marsden, Park Ridge, Regents Park and Crestmead, just to name a few.
 
Berrinba Central is being developed by De Luca Corporation – one of Australia’s leading construction and development companies with over 25 years’ experience in major retail, commercial, industrial, residential and childcare projects.  This experienced developer can work with all tenant requirements to deliver a high-quality.
 
Do not miss this opportunity to be part of this thriving destination amongst major national brands.  For further information, please contact the exclusive CBRE leasing agents, Sam Macgregor and Andrew Brimson.
